(49, 'madagascar', 'p', 'Because we specialize in tours “off the beaten path,” some itineraries include camping experiences. This is the best way to immerse yourself in Madagascar\'s pristine nature, far from crowded tourist areas. We provide modern lightweight tents with excellent waterproof protection (up to 4000 mm water column), ensuring comfort even during tropical rains.', 'Because we specialize in tours “off the beaten path,” some itineraries include camping experiences. This is the best way to immerse yourself in Madagascar\'s pristine nature, far from crowded tourist areas. We provide modern lightweight tents with excellent waterproof protection (up to 4000 mm water column), ensuring comfort even during tropical rains.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(50, 'madagascar', 'p', 'Guests usually sleep in single or double tents, with extra space for luggage and equipment. While camping, our professional cooks prepare three fresh meals daily, with special attention to vegetarian diets and allergy-friendly options. Many travelers say the food served on our camping tours is among the best they enjoy during their entire trip. It\'s a truly memorable way to experience Madagascar\'s landscapes and wilderness.', 'Guests usually sleep in single or double tents, with extra space for luggage and equipment. While camping, our professional cooks prepare three fresh meals daily, with special attention to vegetarian diets and allergy-friendly options. Many travelers say the food served on our camping tours is among the best they enjoy during their entire trip. It\'s a truly memorable way to experience Madagascar\'s landscapes and wilderness.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(51, 'madagascar', 'h3', 'Vehicles - Safe & Reliable Transport Across Madagascar', 'Vehicles - Safe & Reliable Transport Across Madagascar', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(52, 'madagascar', 'p', 'Traveling across Madagascar requires reliable transport, as distances are long and road conditions can be challenging. Our vehicles for Madagascar tours include 4x4 off-road cars, minibuses, and larger buses, depending on group size. Each vehicle meets strict safety standards, is fully insured, and is driven by experienced Malagasy drivers.', 'Traveling across Madagascar requires reliable transport, as distances are long and road conditions can be challenging. Our vehicles for Madagascar tours include 4x4 off-road cars, minibuses, and larger buses, depending on group size. Each vehicle meets strict safety standards, is fully insured, and is driven by experienced Malagasy drivers.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(53, 'madagascar', 'p', 'Our drivers are experts in navigating Madagascar\'s toughest terrains, from rugged highlands to sandy coastal roads. With their knowledge of the country and its landscapes, they guarantee that you will reach your destination safely and comfortably, while also enjoying scenic views along the way.', 'Our drivers are experts in navigating Madagascar\'s toughest terrains, from rugged highlands to sandy coastal roads. With their knowledge of the country and its landscapes, they guarantee that you will reach your destination safely and comfortably, while also enjoying scenic views along the way.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(54, 'madagascar', 'h3', 'Travel Security - Your Safety Comes First', 'Travel Security - Your Safety Comes First', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(55, 'madagascar', 'p', 'When booking a trip, safety and financial protection are essential. Every package tour we offer includes a travel security note, required by European and Swiss law. This guarantees that your prepaid travel expenses are insured in the unlikely event of insolvency by the tour operator.', 'When booking a trip, safety and financial protection are essential. Every package tour we offer includes a travel security note, required by European and Swiss law. This guarantees that your prepaid travel expenses are insured in the unlikely event of insolvency by the tour operator.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
