(16, 'flight-booking', 'Flight booking', 'Reserva de vuelos', 'Madagascar Flight Booking - Easy & Affordable Options', 'Reservas de vuelos a Madagascar - Madagascar Green Tours', 'Book your Madagascar flight easily and affordably today!', 'Reserva tus vuelos a Madagascar fácilmente aquí.', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'best travel, agence de voyage, explore travel, madagascar tourism, madagascar tours, madagascar trip, tour in madagascar, travel tours, private tour', 'img/uploads/images/img_6861a456be8fc1.46392766.webp', 'Flight booking', 'Reserva de vuelos', 'Awesome tours', 'Bienvenido a Madagascar Green Tours', 'Conditions of sale for the tourist services', 'Conditions of sale for the tourist services', '<h4 data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1166\"><strong data-start=\"1120\" data-end=\"1166\">Book Your Flights to and Within Madagascar</strong></h4><p data-start=\"1168\" data-end=\"1428\">Need help booking your flight? We make it easy to travel to Madagascar and explore the island by air. Whether you\'re arriving internationally or flying between cities like Antananarivo, Nosy Be, or Fort Dauphin — we’re here to assist you every step of the way.</p><h4 data-start=\"1430\" data-end=\"1463\"><strong data-start=\"1438\" data-end=\"1463\">International Flights</strong></h4><p data-start=\"1464\" data-end=\"1594\">We help you find and compare the best flights to Madagascar from your country, and assist you with airport pickup once you arrive.</p><h4 data-start=\"1596\" data-end=\"1640\"><strong data-start=\"1606\" data-end=\"1640\">Domestic Flights in Madagascar</strong></h4><p data-start=\"1641\" data-end=\"1746\">Traveling inside Madagascar? Domestic airlines like <strong data-start=\"1693\" data-end=\"1705\">Tsaradia</strong> and <strong data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1728\">Air Madagascar</strong> offer flights to:</p><ul data-start=\"1747\" data